{
  "stem": "2830.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went, I think, to the village or something to look for food or what.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know that half of them disappeared?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Half-- no half of the-- of the-- of the people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whoever had-- had shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean they ran.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They ran away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They run into the forest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They run into the, you know, they were pine forests.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- I remember and they ran.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ones that can still--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Strength.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I looked around, and then I looked around the movie house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was sitting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I took my shoes off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the biggest mistake I ever made.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My feet were very swollen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I couldn't put my-- my-- my feet in anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how swollen  they were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just jiggled in, in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I walked, you know, my heels were out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The laces, I couldn't lace it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's hard walking that way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's how I-- I forced-- I forced-- and then I forced myself walking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forced.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just the pins and the pain, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, and then we started to walk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, we have to continue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't give a damn anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- those-- you know, Werhmacht, whatever they were, they-- the soldiers, they would tired.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were tired.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the dogs, I think, were hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we didn't felt any hunger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't feel any hunger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We felt that we're going to die any minute of starvation and cold, and I swell up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finally, I got to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was in those cars they put us in from, you know, the-- the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was unbelievable what was going on, one on top of each other with-- with feces, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And man and woman, one on top of each other, the screaming, the hunger.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
